text.tspan: * ADC : 12-bit SAR ADC up to 18 channels @ 6Khz
* Driverless Drag and drop programming of ESP32 & SAML21
* Traditional USB serial interface still present
* I2C IO Expansion Interface for ESP32 to SAML21
* AES Engine & True Random Number Generator
* LED Bus Header for driving up to 1020 LEDS @ 30fps.
